741
00:49:25,883 --> 00:49:28,883
The next step, of course-

742
00:49:29,987 --> 00:49:32,987
You know, it wasn't my goal
to start an industry.

743
00:49:33,590 --> 00:49:36,590
My goal was to, um,
make sure the science
got translated...

744
00:49:38,495 --> 00:49:41,495
