00:54:10,067 --> 00:54:13,067
The two of them did not make
a good impression on people.

803
00:54:13,971 --> 00:54:16,971
They were bearded.
They didn't smell good.

804
00:54:17,007 --> 00:54:20,007
They dressed funny.
Young, naive.

