that if you have a serious partner,
a good partner, who says,
"I just don't see this"-

932
01:02:50,353 --> 01:02:51,987
How can you proceed?

933
01:02:51,988 --> 01:02:54,988
As a matter of policy, we wouldn't
permit that in our place.

934
