as PowerPoint.

948
01:03:55,218 --> 01:03:58,218
And they would like to acquire us
and kill their own project."

949
01:03:59,956 --> 01:04:02,956
I said, "If that's
the way you want to go,
it's okay with me."

950
01:04:07,630 --> 01:04:10,630
Another one of my greatest mistakes,
of which I have many,

951
01:04:12,235 --> 01:04:15,235
is when Microsoft
did the acquisition,
they wanted to do it all in stock.

952
01:04:18,374 --> 01:04:21,374
So I was, like, "Oh, you know,
Microsoft stock
has way too much risk.

953
01:04:22,579 --> 01:04:25,447
They could dump their stock
on us at their peak!"

954
01:04:25,448 --> 01:04:28,448
So we did an all-cash transaction.

