966
01:05:18,868 --> 01:05:21,236
change presidents in 18 months.

967
01:05:21,237 --> 01:05:24,072
I mean, I always tell
the young C.E.O.'s,
you're gonna work hard,

968
01:05:24,073 --> 01:05:26,408
and you're gonna, you know,
if you're lucky,

969
01:05:26,409 --> 01:05:28,610
you're gonna be successful,
and your company's
