970
01:05:28,611 --> 01:05:31,611
And then you're gonna get fired.

971
01:05:33,650 --> 01:05:36,551
Firing people is always
the hardest for me.

972
01:05:36,552 --> 01:05:38,220
That's a gut-wrenching
thing to do.

973
01:05:38,221 --> 01:05:39,888
If they gotta go, they gotta go.

974
01:05:39,889 --> 01:05:42,889
I'd rather find the right people
and back them,

975
01:05:44,594 --> 01:05:47,594
uh, than find the right idea
and have to change the people.

976
01:05:49,032 --> 01:05:52,032
Well, nobody plans to do that,
